<subSubSection pageId="41" pageNumber="640" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="41.[1446,2654,1752,2454]" pageId="41" pageNumber="640">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1446,1683,2224,2258]" pageId="41" pageNumber="640">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Somali Pygmy Gerbil is nocturnal and terrestrial, probably digging burrows or resting by day under rock crevices.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
